## 8. Checklist — before you promise HA + Citus in an interview

- [ ] **RPO/RTO** for failover (async vs sync).
- [ ] **Who** runs failover (Patroni vs cloud vs operator).
- [ ] **Citus** topology: N workers, **replication factor**, **coordinator** HA.
- [ ] **Sharding key** chosen with **product** — not only DBA.
- [ ] **Backups** per node + **restore drill**.
- [ ] **Monitoring:** replication lag, **disk**, **connections**, **Citus** rebalancer, **vacuum** age.

